Message Tracer

Messages.Mod is a display message tracer for ETH Oberon.  It can be useful 
when developing handler procedures.  Simply insert a Messages.Log(m) call at 
the relevant place in your message handler.  When the module is loaded, a 
message log text will appear.  The log can be re-opened with the
Messages.OpenLog call.

